---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Contact Us"
  description="How to reach the PoE2 Hub team with corrections, suggestions, or questions about the site."
>
  <h1>Contact Us</h1>

  <p>
    Spotted an error, have a suggestion, or want to get in touch? Email us
    at <a href="mailto:contact@poe2hub.net">contact@poe2hub.net</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Corrections are especially welcome. If a number or mechanic on any page
    looks wrong, tell us which page and which patch you are playing on, and we
    will re-verify it against the sources.
  </p>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  p { color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.75; }
</style>
